lead_paragraph: No extra security is planned at the finish line of the world's most famous sled dog race, just days after a man on a snowmobile purposely drove at a high speed into two mushers' teams, killing one dog and injuring several others.

headline.main: No Extra Security Planned as Iditarod Nears Nome Finish
